flowRoot.flowPara: XMPP based publish-subscribe mechanism to exchange security-relevant information between network endpoints.
Based on IEFT MILE standard draft:
Using XMPP for Security Information Exchange
Focus on: Portability, extensibility and security
XMPP from the web browser with Stanza.io
Broker usually communicates with XMPP ser-ver over a proxy, which also hosts the broker
